<hr local-id=3D"7e3d6ff29784">
<h2 local-id=3D"cc997e3c6c2e" id=3D"Task21-TechnicalDocument-4.DevelopmentP=
ractices">4. Development Practices</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"c518ec8c4610" id=3D"Task21-TechnicalDocument-4.1VersionCont=
rol">4.1 Version Control</h3>
<p local-id=3D"3a8d3da981ed">The Hello World application was deployed direc=
tly to Azure App Service for this PoC. No version control integration was c=
onfigured in this task.</p>
<p local-id=3D"bea328253144"><strong>Recommended production version control=
 setup:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"43a8777ae4ea">
<li local-id=3D"0985c3698231">
<p local-id=3D"093782a732ba">Host application code in a Git repository (Git=
Hub, GitLab, or Azure Repos)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fe52a2c6c803">
<p local-id=3D"a327a53ed91f">Connect Azure App Service Deployment Center to=
 the repository for automated deployments on push</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"65f544b8c1d6">
<p local-id=3D"9990250df105">Use branch-based deployments: <code>main</code=
> =E2=86=92 production slot, <code>develop</code> =E2=86=92 staging slot</p=
></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"fd367c0c6239" id=3D"Task21-TechnicalDocument-4.2ContinuousI=
ntegration">4.2 Continuous Integration</h3>
<p local-id=3D"85e95cb3c3ad">CI was not configured in this PoC. The focus w=
as on infrastructure provisioning and DNS configuration.</p>
<p local-id=3D"6164dd6fcbce"><strong>Recommended future CI setup:</strong><=
/p>
<ul local-id=3D"90653a0b3d44">
<li local-id=3D"2682def390c5">
<p local-id=3D"f22f1fff7807">Use Azure DevOps Pipelines or GitHub Actions f=
or automated build and test on code push</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3c036a15e04e">
<p local-id=3D"40392b084aca">Define a pipeline YAML file (<code>azure-pipel=
ines.yml</code> or <code>.github/workflows/deploy.yml</code>)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"353b5188839c">
<p local-id=3D"e7afc3d5a82d">Automate Python dependency installation, linti=
ng, and unit test execution before deployment</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"ee0c5962177d" id=3D"Task21-TechnicalDocument-4.3AutomatedTe=
sting">4.3 Automated Testing</h3>
<p local-id=3D"b20677aee28a">Automated testing was not implemented in this =
PoC.</p>
<p local-id=3D"46420bfd5924"><strong>Recommended future testing setup:</str=
ong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"230ae316a465">
<li local-id=3D"14c4f525d307">
<p local-id=3D"e919d80cb3ac">Unit tests using <code>pytest</code> for the P=
ython Hello World application</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"552577fe42fb">
<p local-id=3D"35dc8411ce0b">End-to-end tests validating the HTTP response =
from both the default Azure URL and the custom domain</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"21da54431909">
<p local-id=3D"85e3a7267521">Integrate tests into the Azure DevOps pipeline=
 as a pre-deployment gate</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"15d420ac3011" id=3D"Task21-TechnicalDocument-4.4CodeQuality=
andAnalysis">4.4 Code Quality and Analysis</h3>
<p local-id=3D"a7e581024026">Code quality tooling was not configured in thi=
s PoC.</p>
<p local-id=3D"5db06dfd1873"><strong>Recommended future setup:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"a57fc587a3da">
<li local-id=3D"d06ea1703fe0">
<p local-id=3D"b2aa0c337399"><code>flake8</code> or <code>pylint</code> for=
 Python static code analysis</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ce74d317b490">
<p local-id=3D"f6580f04f6fb"><code>black</code> for Python code formatting<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"dbf1a6a303d9">
<p local-id=3D"34b1e437c1b3">Azure DevOps pipeline quality gates to block d=
eployments failing code quality checks</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"d7fda2e657d4">
<h2 local-id=3D"0ae80bcf104c" id=3D"Task21-TechnicalDocument-5.Deploymentan=
dReleaseManagement">5. Deployment and Release Management</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"5261fec62305" id=3D"Task21-TechnicalDocument-5.1DeploymentS=
trategy">5.1 Deployment Strategy</h3>
<p local-id=3D"efb5dae8195d">For this PoC, the Hello World application was =
deployed directly to the Azure App Service production slot via the Azure Po=
rtal. No formal deployment pipeline was implemented.</p>
<p local-id=3D"73ccf65ed29d"><strong>Application details deployed:</strong>=
</p>
<ul local-id=3D"8434356050ec">
<li local-id=3D"e6eb524415a8">
<p local-id=3D"0836ca948f6c">App Name: <code>karna-app-service</code></p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"4a6d9a0a9af6">
<p local-id=3D"011e030ab36e">Runtime: Python 3.14</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f5b0a07182ad">
<p local-id=3D"4376495f3ceb">OS: Linux</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1d494ca9d76b">
<p local-id=3D"322a183bfd9a">Publishing Model: Code</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"06ffb17de643">
<p local-id=3D"ac4c688cc62d">Status: Running / Healthy</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"20d1fa2e7ff5"><strong>Recommended production deployment stra=
tegy:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"ab246da5e48b">
<li local-id=3D"87588f395b1b">
<p local-id=3D"fafc5e340acf">Use Azure App Service Deployment Slots (stagin=
g =E2=86=92 production swap)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"afd881d866a7">
<p local-id=3D"fef1b346d9ea">Implement blue-green deployments using slot sw=
apping for zero-downtime releases</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7d9586a654b6">
<p local-id=3D"61da112dcfac">Use Azure DevOps Release Pipelines with approv=
al gates for production deployments</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"79500c0c2d9d" id=3D"Task21-TechnicalDocument-5.2Configurati=
onManagement">5.2 Configuration Management</h3>
<p local-id=3D"23b9f5fefb49">Azure App Service configuration is managed thr=
ough the Azure Portal under the App Service settings.</p>
