<h3 local-id=3D"116de664e3b6" id=3D"Task21-TechnicalDocument-5.3ContinuousD=
eliveryandDeployment">5.3 Continuous Delivery and Deployment</h3>
<p local-id=3D"3f27723db11d">CD was not implemented in this PoC. The applic=
ation was manually deployed through the Azure Portal.</p>
<p local-id=3D"4217433fa925"><strong>Recommended future CD setup:</strong><=
/p>
<ul local-id=3D"1ec96c8c57bc">
<li local-id=3D"7a421c4ee7af">
<p local-id=3D"c0661d23f8e5">Azure DevOps Release Pipeline auto-deploys on =
successful CI build</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bc0414a7dd86">
<p local-id=3D"01342e4afa8c">Deployment to staging slot first, with manual =
approval for production slot swap</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1d3cd7d2ce9e">
<p local-id=3D"aac6d2d3089f">Rollback strategy: swap slots back if issues a=
re detected post-deployment</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"0daf8ebcfa99">
<h2 local-id=3D"317bbac04dd9" id=3D"Task21-TechnicalDocument-6.Monitoringan=
dIncidentManagement">6. Monitoring and Incident Management</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"3be5a5f2e4a1" id=3D"Task21-TechnicalDocument-6.1MonitoringT=
oolsandMetrics">6.1 Monitoring Tools and Metrics</h3>
<p local-id=3D"ee0f20facfd9">For this PoC, the Health Check in Azure App Se=
rvice was noted as "Not Configured." The App Service shows a runtime status=
 of "Healthy" confirming the application is running.</p>
<p local-id=3D"36d3a577c419"><strong>Built-in Azure App Service monitoring =
available:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"ef8d376dacae">
<li local-id=3D"558a40e3d8ad">
<p local-id=3D"bb84498a6f24">Azure Portal =E2=86=92 App Service =E2=86=92 M=
onitoring =E2=86=92 Metrics (CPU, Memory, HTTP requests)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a3bdfcb2dc02">
<p local-id=3D"8bc354e2b4bd">Azure Portal =E2=86=92 App Service =E2=86=92 L=
og stream (real-time application logs)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2e9f95c3f267">
<p local-id=3D"cee7f2ef1d53">Azure Portal =E2=86=92 App Service =E2=86=92 D=
iagnose and solve problems</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"aafa72801fde"><strong>Recommended production monitoring setu=
p:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"e253ae88746b">
<li local-id=3D"a8c146c8a1b2">
<p local-id=3D"a5115c4d76d5">Enable Application Insights for deep applicati=
on performance monitoring</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b1db9878b6a0">
<p local-id=3D"472a56984b9d">Configure Health Check endpoint in App Service=
 settings</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a4f3360db853">
<p local-id=3D"c70480f38476">Set up Azure Monitor Alerts for CPU &gt; 80%, =
HTTP 5xx errors, and response time &gt; 2 seconds</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"50e618387022" id=3D"Task21-TechnicalDocument-6.2Alertingand=
Notification">6.2 Alerting and Notification</h3>
<p local-id=3D"57f0590359eb">No alerting was configured for this PoC.</p>
<p local-id=3D"b36dadca29c8"><strong>Recommended production alerting:</stro=
ng></p>
<ul local-id=3D"a30e60dcdb33">
<li local-id=3D"297d39c3d9a8">
<p local-id=3D"2166b9933096">Azure Monitor Alerts triggered on metric thres=
holds</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0a9e83dcb9cc">
<p local-id=3D"1dba20fde474">Action Groups configured to send email/SMS to =
the DevOps team</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"be142fd75bfc">
<p local-id=3D"83331a44e5b9">Integration with PagerDuty or Slack for critic=
al incident escalation</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"8fdbeadda655" id=3D"Task21-TechnicalDocument-6.3IncidentMan=
agement">6.3 Incident Management</h3>
<p local-id=3D"7c8b1a938fea">No formal incident management process was impl=
emented for this PoC.</p>
<p local-id=3D"9e3a71a38ba5"><strong>Recommended production incident manage=
ment:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"c=
29544d5-9700-46ec-aebc-0318dd2d856f" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"e6cec76fc346">
<th data-local-id=3D"352195336172" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"371953306e72">Step</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"907479bfde83" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"0d2b49f41202">Action</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"1012a6a19d37">
<td data-local-id=3D"41c200c0ab85" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"bf878af4a084">Detection</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e2db725122fe" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c6d325c9fa4a">Azure Monitor alert or Application Insights an=
omaly triggers</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"d8d38a883d42">
<td data-local-id=3D"c321cfb4cee4" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0fb8034608c5">Notification</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"d83c896105d6" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e9c448af2521">Alert sent to DevOps on-call via email/Slack</=
p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"649bfda9f436">
<td data-local-id=3D"df05c73e4b71" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a8c5e9e5e90d">Triage</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e7aa5bd8cbba" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"e5420af364be">DevOps engineer checks App Service logs and me=
trics</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"43601b2f6359">
<td data-local-id=3D"3ba88ebaa71d" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5fe3c60dfc83">Resolution</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"aaa92cb67166" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8255cbb79af9">Restart App Service, swap deployment slots, or=
 roll back code</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"890eede4c138">
<td data-local-id=3D"06585d91028c" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2c73d4c1f432">Post-mortem</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"bc2e5638b698" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a81de1192d86">Root cause documented; preventive measures imp=
lemented</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"f853c374a502">
<h2 local-id=3D"89e7a82ba5b9" id=3D"Task21-TechnicalDocument-7.SecurityandC=
ompliance">7. Security and Compliance</h2>
