<p local-id=3D"0ff2c7c157e9"><strong>Recommended additional security harden=
ing:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"ed78b5ac1913">
<li local-id=3D"ef206e619a81">
<p local-id=3D"7ac8ead139ba">Enable Managed Identity for the App Service to=
 authenticate to other Azure services without credentials</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"31fdb703dc07">
<p local-id=3D"dc18ce3a0284">Configure IP restrictions in App Service to li=
mit access to known IP ranges</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7199fd3da997">
<p local-id=3D"8ec2a6619807">Enable HTTPS Only setting in App Service to re=
ject all HTTP requests</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2b883e61d032">
<p local-id=3D"f44d82f1d167">Add a custom SSL certificate for the <code>app=
.karna.pushkar.cloud</code> domain to remove the "Not Secure" browser warni=
ng</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"55aaef95b237">
<p local-id=3D"0a0aa800bc2d">Enable Azure Defender for App Service for thre=
at detection</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"3c8e5873fafe">
<h2 local-id=3D"f2d6d303b734" id=3D"Task21-TechnicalDocument-8.CostOptimiza=
tion">8. Cost Optimization</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"ed3cd12d3460" id=3D"Task21-TechnicalDocument-8.1TotalCostof=
Ownership(TCO)Analysis">8.1 Total Cost of Ownership (TCO) Analysis</h3>
<p local-id=3D"31c8e27ac43b"><strong>Inputs Used to Estimate Solution Cost:=
</strong></p>
