<h3 local-id=3D"55b610366898" id=3D"Task21-TechnicalDocument-8.2CostOptimiz=
ationRecommendations">8.2 Cost Optimization Recommendations</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"be04d67d9f21">
<li local-id=3D"fd332124565d">
<p local-id=3D"74e92ec82573"><strong>Right-sizing:</strong> P0v3 is appropr=
iate for a PoC; in production, monitor CPU and memory metrics before scalin=
g up</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9c58599f4baf">
<p local-id=3D"ccd051707615"><strong>Free Tier for Dev/Test:</strong> Use A=
zure App Service Free (F1) tier for development and testing environments to=
 eliminate compute costs</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"06ce1518d766">
<p local-id=3D"64b1123040eb"><strong>Auto-scaling:</strong> Configure App S=
ervice Plan auto-scale rules to scale in during off-peak hours</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"39ce79fa6654">
<p local-id=3D"6ac85da95152"><strong>Reserved Capacity:</strong> For produc=
tion workloads, commit to 1-year reserved App Service Plan pricing for ~35%=
 savings</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f7b9b92c34b4">
<p local-id=3D"f851700f1105"><strong>DNS Cost:</strong> Route 53 hosted zon=
e cost is fixed at $0.50/month regardless of record count; no optimization =
needed</p></li>
</ul>
