<h2 local-id=3D"92c4baca2631" id=3D"Task21-TechnicalDocument-10.Implementat=
ionTimeline">10. Implementation Timeline</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"e87d2e63034f" id=3D"Task21-TechnicalDocument-10.1Milestones=
andDeliverables">10.1 Milestones and Deliverables</h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"7=
d792335-6050-415a-a120-482193da0aa6" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"58e7f6a98e34">
<th data-local-id=3D"3df5722858e8" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"518ef6ec7835">Phase</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"345aabca9ab7" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"15e985caac7a">Tasks</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"7d0e27083acc" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"3cfa486773a9">Duration</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"e1acbd5d73ac">
<td data-local-id=3D"653ac2961b4b" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2a70e7cc8eb4"><strong>Phase 1: Azure App Service Creation</s=
trong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"8bb66566be6f" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ff153779a9b9">Log in to Azure Portal, create App Service Pla=
n (P0v3, Linux), create Web App (karna-app-service, Python 3.14, Central US=
), verify default domain is accessible</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"170f72737f60" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"260660bdd1d0">20=E2=80=9330 minutes</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"864e1afc29a2">
<td data-local-id=3D"a7432ce518ab" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"957f4c2611e8"><strong>Phase 2: Hello World Application Deplo=
yment</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ee9e7e7e0f65" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a4cb4ef8e30f">Deploy Hello World application to App Service,=
 verify "Hello World from Azure!" response at the default Azure URL, confir=
m runtime status is Healthy</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b31ddf4b89fb" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"edac6abbb9ed">15=E2=80=9320 minutes</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"f59bf77b7f43">
<td data-local-id=3D"97f0952fc333" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"332d404b2524"><strong>Phase 3: DNS Record Creation in AWS Ro=
ute 53</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"8320261db99c" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"fe8ed7f4e679">Navigate to Route 53 hosted zone (karna.pushka=
r.cloud), create CNAME record (app =E2=86=92 Azure default domain), create =
TXT record (asuid.app =E2=86=92 Azure verification ID), set TTL to 300 seco=
nds</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"8bbf5de304cd" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"63afcd815824">15=E2=80=9320 minutes</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"aa2b26a6941e">
<td data-local-id=3D"3dc1934c9f30" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"59710acc0bbb"><strong>Phase 4: Custom Domain Mapping in Azur=
e</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ee6b59eaa3f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"566b1487bd0b">Add custom domain <code>app.karna.pushkar.clou=
d</code> in Azure App Service Custom Domains, validate domain ownership via=
 TXT record, confirm custom domain is active</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"32c6fd4a9436" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"aadc9768e966">15=E2=80=9320 minutes</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"0a8052e75e03">
<td data-local-id=3D"c9f2a6de0c72" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ffead49db8ec"><strong>Phase 5: DNS Validation</strong></p></=
td>
<td data-local-id=3D"dfb7367e3ec6" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ebe31c5f1398">Run <code>nslookup -type=3DTXT asuid.app.karna=
.pushkar.cloud</code> to verify TXT record, run <code>nslookup app.karna.pu=
shkar.cloud</code> to verify CNAME resolution, confirm IP resolves to Azure=
 (40.122.36.65)</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"9de422c09006" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ccfff31547f7">10=E2=80=9315 minutes</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"ccb56c6ab1ee">
<td data-local-id=3D"dcf5e2c22b5d" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9bf6ebc33c67"><strong>Phase 6: SOA Record Inspection</strong=
></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"130ebdc0431c" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b1356445c180">Run <code>nslookup -type=3DSOA karna.pushkar.c=
loud</code> to retrieve SOA record, document all 7 SOA fields (MNAME, RNAME=
, SERIAL, REFRESH, RETRY, EXPIRE, MIN TTL) with explanations</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b5e1fb8acbfb" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"0ffc08c2455b">10=E2=80=9315 minutes</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"4b617f08a889">
<td data-local-id=3D"7ab5bb47ca96" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"633454a7138e"><strong>Phase 7: Validation &amp; Documentatio=
n</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"0b7d083f32c3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5bdc6961179c">Verify Hello World app via custom domain in br=
owser, capture all required screenshots, prepare technical documentation</p=
></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"82532aa4f47d" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"90920ca0da4c">20=E2=80=9330 minutes</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"ee63541d8e3b">
<td data-local-id=3D"00718ca427a5" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b32b3024693a"><strong>Total</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"23cb1b805890" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ce7782e03340"></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"0b774dbe4a75" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cb4bcc8f9296"><strong>~2=E2=80=933 Hours</strong></p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"61a2a3d64057">
<h2 local-id=3D"84b08595d756" id=3D"Task21-TechnicalDocument-11.ContinuousI=
mprovement">11. Continuous Improvement</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"4a32cb6e7c2c" id=3D"Task21-TechnicalDocument-11.1Feedbackan=
dRetrospectives">11.1 Feedback and Retrospectives</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"7e527718480f">
<li local-id=3D"4c0b4d648e7d">
<p local-id=3D"c3ce6cd9c675">Post-implementation review to identify frictio=
n points: the "Not Secure" browser warning on the custom domain was noted a=
s a gap requiring a custom SSL certificate</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8664eae1bad1">
<p local-id=3D"b74c86de4e3a">Key learning: TXT record must be created at <c=
ode>asuid.&lt;subdomain&gt;</code> (not <code>&lt;subdomain&gt;</code>) for=
 Azure domain verification =E2=80=94 this is a specific Azure requirement t=
hat differs from other platforms</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b16b9185c78b">
<p local-id=3D"3844f10c9548">DNS propagation with TTL of 300 seconds requir=
ed a short wait before validation commands returned correct results</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"3b0477091d00">
<p local-id=3D"550d43de83fe">Recommended for future iterations: pre-create =
the TXT record before starting the Azure domain mapping to reduce waiting t=
ime</p></li>
</ul>
