<hr local-id=3D"2ac43ebb9fa5">
<h2 local-id=3D"c0b150245cbf" id=3D"Task21-TechnicalDocument-12.Conclusion"=
>12. Conclusion</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"f1e13873feba" id=3D"Task21-TechnicalDocument-12.1Summary">1=
2.1 Summary</h3>
<p local-id=3D"1ed045df027f">This document has detailed the end-to-end tech=
nical implementation of an Azure App Service deployment with custom domain =
mapping for ABC Technologies. The key achievements of this implementation a=
re:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"ae76bacabf50">
<li local-id=3D"bf03e627d807">
<p local-id=3D"ef8b1ec27d57">A fully functional Hello World application dep=
loyed on Azure App Service (Python 3.14, Linux, Central US) with a runtime =
status of Healthy</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f730ff9b6fc8">
<p local-id=3D"15a344891c54">The application accessible via the default Azu=
re URL: <code>karna-app-service-grf3c8due9efcdg9.centralus-01.azurewebsites=
.net</code></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ce6fa15341e3">
<p local-id=3D"982aa6ee02a0">CNAME and TXT DNS records created in AWS Route=
 53 to map <code>app.karna.pushkar.cloud</code> to the Azure App Service</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"293b1e1d0d5f">
<p local-id=3D"7bb823a805e4">Custom domain <code>app.karna.pushkar.cloud</c=
ode> successfully mapped and validated in Azure App Service</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d870cd7898b8">
<p local-id=3D"7752810bf1ff">DNS resolution verified using <code>nslookup</=
code> confirming CNAME resolution to the Azure backend IP (40.122.36.65)</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"0c922fded95b">
<p local-id=3D"a4ee71347426">SOA record documented with all 7 fields explai=
ned in detail</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"47ef17454cf8">
<p local-id=3D"3daf1741d413">Microsoft-managed SSL certificate confirmed on=
 the default Azure domain (issued by Microsoft Azure RSA TLS Issuing CA 07)=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"09a6100c5552">
<p local-id=3D"57dae4698c3b">AWS Well-Architected Framework principles appl=
ied across all 6 pillars</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"7c191eaa498e" id=3D"Task21-TechnicalDocument-12.2NextSteps"=
>12.2 Next Steps</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"8be2c705fd31">
<li local-id=3D"a3aa493ebbde">
<p local-id=3D"8c049eb31926"><strong>Immediate:</strong> Add a custom SSL c=
ertificate to <code>app.karna.pushkar.cloud</code> to resolve the browser "=
Not Secure" warning</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"81441e936776">
<p local-id=3D"bbea9954b022"><strong>Immediate:</strong> Enable "HTTPS Only=
" in Azure App Service settings to enforce secure access</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9c8b14939d69">
<p local-id=3D"386d76cb550d"><strong>Short-term:</strong> Connect Azure App=
 Service Deployment Center to a GitHub repository for automated code deploy=
ments</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"eb80dadcc8c9">
<p local-id=3D"12ad1e3ca9e3"><strong>Short-term:</strong> Enable Applicatio=
n Insights for monitoring application performance and errors</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7f55c96cdd91">
<p local-id=3D"54d8bfdf0498"><strong>Medium-term:</strong> Configure a Heal=
th Check endpoint and Azure Monitor Alerts for proactive incident detection=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"634440877c68">
<p local-id=3D"f6076942477b"><strong>Medium-term:</strong> Add a staging de=
ployment slot for blue-green deployments</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"748699863ee6">
<p local-id=3D"45f3ca3b12a2"><strong>Long-term:</strong> Explore Azure Fron=
t Door or Azure CDN for global content delivery and enhanced custom domain =
SSL management</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"03ddfbd62209">
<h2 local-id=3D"d11adb938ce9" id=3D"Task21-TechnicalDocument-13.CustomerAck=
