<hr local-id=3D"4b7d0c40d7a3">
<h2 local-id=3D"1e88b1226ee5" id=3D"Task21-TechnicalDocument-AppendixC:DNSV=
alidationCommandsandResults">Appendix C: DNS Validation Commands and Result=
s</h2>
<p local-id=3D"c3789e5b6953"><strong>TXT Record Verification (PowerShell):<=
/strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">nslooku=
p -type=3DTXT asuid.app.karna.pushkar.cloud

Result:
asuid.app.karna.pushkar.cloud  text =3D
"4F56E2DED9F8828991B87FE61AFAE9B29DBDA673AC84C957EED4876CD6DC66E9"</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"c0f5438a6b15"><strong>CNAME Resolution Verification (PowerSh=
ell):</strong></p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">nslooku=
p app.karna.pushkar.cloud

Result:
Name:     waws-prod-dm1-135.centralus.cloudapp.azure.com
Addresses: 64:ff9b::287a:2441
           40.122.36.65
Aliases:   app.karna.pushkar.cloud
           karna-app-service-grf3c8due9efcdg9.centralus-01.azurewebsites.ne=
t
           waws-prod-dm1-135.sip.azurewebsites.windows.net</pre>
</div>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"18f6d2cc31aa">Both DNS validations confirm the records are c=
orrectly propagated and resolving as expected.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"223dd24c74c8">
<h2 local-id=3D"2b1b37b84b6a" id=3D"Task21-TechnicalDocument-AppendixD:Diff=
erenceBetweenSOAandTXTRecords">Appendix D: Difference Between SOA and TXT R=
ecords</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"8=
6e99337-9db2-4b91-8143-e032288352c4" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"05a4a20c6bc2">
<th data-local-id=3D"9d149fc06058" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"999f75722dd4">Aspect</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"4a2128320dc1" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"564e500f73a0">SOA Record</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"f730c9122cfd" class=3D"confluenceTh">
<p local-id=3D"cfdc52a5be45">TXT Record</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"95cd2be24db9">
<td data-local-id=3D"787625d9cdf7" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8ec4c1e64b9f">Full Name</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"16b0a5d96802" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a76c0922ed8a">Start of Authority</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"aa3fda9450a7" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"7c92c28e0a92">Text Record</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"010c11cf0279">
<td data-local-id=3D"487e7fd13592" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8a00c91dd153">Primary Purpose</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"02314af82291" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"dca17b6173a1">Defines the authoritative DNS server and zone =
management parameters</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"529bbe84b0d8" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"67006137c709">Stores arbitrary text data; used for domain ve=
rification, SPF, DKIM, and other validations</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"b9e3b8c6d9ce">
<td data-local-id=3D"4aef6ca36807" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b12eaec692d0">Who Creates It</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"8fa8f37022f5" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2f0e9bed5dfe">Automatically created by the DNS provider when=
 a hosted zone is created</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"bff6dbab7fc0" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"947358082155">Manually created by the domain administrator</=
p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"1871173dcffc">
<td data-local-id=3D"e7b0c6be2d8a" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c0b12023e711">Example Use</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"22a9573a6227" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"a3b22fe0dc49">Defines primary nameserver, admin contact, ref=
resh intervals</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"56c69d1c3829" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"deaaff8eadde">Azure domain ownership verification, Google Se=
arch Console verification, email SPF records</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"c1feb1e55a1d">
<td data-local-id=3D"aca51bcca974" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"4c9e206b2dd2">Uniqueness</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"e8fe1e0e036e" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"b0aae03606d5">Only one SOA record per DNS zone</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"423f3198208f" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"f59b49718ef6">Multiple TXT records can exist in a zone</p></=
td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"2b4dae5158e3">
<td data-local-id=3D"50a54915ef94" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c11db221e3ef">In This Task</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"3a76f04ff0f9" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"dd8dd870c4a0">Inspected to understand DNS zone authority and=
 replication settings</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"fbde884fc845" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p local-id=3D"fcef94407fda">Created at <code>asuid.app.karna.pushkar.cloud=
</code> to verify domain ownership before Azure mapped the custom domain</p=
></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"661641cc1ef8">
<h2 local-id=3D"b5f0d75aeadf" id=3D"Task21-TechnicalDocument-AppendixE:Howt=
oConnectAzureAppServicetoaCustomDomain">Appendix E: How to Connect Azure Ap=
p Service to a Custom Domain</h2>
<p local-id=3D"7b787db268c3"><strong>Step 1: Get the Azure Verification ID<=
/strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"4ccbd334f503">
<li local-id=3D"b448158b4b6d">
<p local-id=3D"49aaefb320bf">In Azure Portal, go to the App Service =E2=86=
=92 Settings =E2=86=92 Custom Domains</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e77b520cee06">
<p local-id=3D"26528e1f7b27">Click "Add custom domain" and enter the custom=
 domain (e.g., <code>app.karna.pushkar.cloud</code>)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bb108e7cfa10">
<p local-id=3D"07e99a58bdfa">Azure will provide a verification ID (used for=
 the TXT record)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"5f7cea7ea774"><strong>Step 2: Create DNS Records in Route 53=
</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"991bac373064">
<li local-id=3D"4612ce0080a2">
<p local-id=3D"04a1f88d238e">Go to AWS Route 53 =E2=86=92 Hosted Zones =E2=
=86=92 karna.pushkar.cloud</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9510f59ed189">
<p local-id=3D"c90b3534f619">Create CNAME record: <code>app</code> =E2=86=
=92 <code>&lt;azure-default-domain&gt;.azurewebsites.net</code> (TTL: 300)<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"731924165769">
<p local-id=3D"d76330b1c1af">Create TXT record: <code>asuid.app</code> =E2=
=86=92 <code>&lt;Azure Verification ID&gt;</code> (TTL: 300)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fb8b5765e914">
<p local-id=3D"5f37f30b49c1">Wait for DNS propagation (typically 1=E2=80=93=
5 minutes with TTL 300)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"0020a97a61c3"><strong>Step 3: Validate and Add the Custom Do=
main in Azure</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"8a52e6d3d049">
<li local-id=3D"c6a8e7526478">
<p local-id=3D"b8318aee4139">Return to Azure Portal =E2=86=92 App Service =
=E2=86=92 Custom Domains</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e6c9b6a8e051">
<p local-id=3D"79c2ec696472">Click "Validate" =E2=80=94 Azure checks the TX=
T record for domain ownership</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9edaeb300244">
<p local-id=3D"d4c824eec9d3">Once validated, click "Add custom domain"</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"f373e9a4d6f8">
<p local-id=3D"6beed632c685">The custom domain is now mapped and the applic=
ation is accessible via the custom URL</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"e8a52f46e404"><strong>Step 4: Verify</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"e35a1dbb1700">
<li local-id=3D"a9ea7efbab0a">
<p local-id=3D"46230054fa7a">Open <code>https://app.karna.pushkar.cloud</co=
de> in a browser</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b2d78ad5ac9d">
<p local-id=3D"4c3176870aa5">Confirm "Hello World from Azure!" is displayed=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0e5684756481">
<p local-id=3D"fe8e560749c8">Run <code>nslookup app.karna.pushkar.cloud</co=
de> in PowerShell to confirm DNS resolution</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"23dbb9aec587"></p>
<p local-id=3D"a34fb7bf8111"></p>
<p local-id=3D"51208d137aef"></p>
<p local-id=3D"44003a93cd80"></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
